name: .RRBB File Extension
summary: Learn about .RRBB files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: Because RRBB files are encrypted, you cannot open them. Currently, there is no way to decrypt RRBB files.

To recover your files, you should retrieve them from a recent backup or perform a System Restore. Note that performing a System Restore will cause you to lose any files created since your last restore point. You may want to back up these files before performing a System Restore.
